  | volume = 8
  | pages = 30
  | year = 1949
  | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1949MNSSA...8...30T
  | accessdate = 2010-02-27
  | archive-date = 2020-07-08
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200708005808/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1949MNSSA...8...30T/abstract
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>

==物理特性==

珠宝盒星团是目前已知最年轻的疏散星团之一。<ref name="JudgeToyne">{{Cite book
  | last = Judge
  | first = Harry George
  | coauthors = Toyne, Anthony
  | title = Oxford Illustrated Encyclopedia, Volume 8
  | year = 1993
  | pages = 76
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=4UgUAQAAIAAJ&q=%22jewel+box+cluster%22&dq=%22jewel+box+cluster%22&cd=7
  | access-date = 2010-07-24
  | archive-date = 2011-06-10
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110610053156/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=4UgUAQAAIAAJ&q=%22jewel+box+cluster%22&dq=%22jewel+box+cluster%22&cd=7
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref> 其中最著名的就是发出明亮橙色光的[[恒星光谱|M型]][[超巨星|红超巨星]][[南十字座κ|南十字座κ]]，它和星团中大部分发出蓝色光的热恒星形成鲜明对比。事实上，星团中的明亮成员恒星都是超巨星，其中有一些是目前已知[[银河系|银河系]]最明亮的恒星之一。<ref name="Burnham">{{Cite book
  | last = Burnham
  | first = Robert
  | title = Burnham's Celestial Handbook: An Observer's Guide to the Universe Beyond the Solar System
  | publisher = Dover Publications
  | year = 1978
  | location = New York
  | pages = 730
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=wB9uZ9lH5bgC&pg=PA730&dq=%22kappa+crucis%22+cluster&lr=&cd=12#v=onepage&q=%22kappa%20crucis%22%20cluster&f=false
}}</ref>

珠宝盒星团的平均[[径向速度|径向速度]]是每秒钟向我们靠近17.9[[公里|公里]]。<ref name="Feast">{{Cite journal
  | last = Feast
  | first = M. W.
  | title = The galactic cluster NGC 4755 (κ Crucis)
  | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society
  | volume = 126
  | pages = 11
  | year = 1963
  | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1963MNRAS.126...11F
  | accessdate = 2010-02-27
  | archive-date = 2015-03-16
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150316071234/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1963MNRAS.126...11F
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>由于星团在天球的投影和著名的[[暗星云|暗星云]][[煤袋星云|煤袋星云]]邻近（虽然两者的实际距离可能非常遥远，但从地球上看，珠宝盒星团就刚好位于煤袋星云侧后方），它发出的光部分会被星云所遮挡，因此准确计算出它的距离就变得非常困难，<ref name="ConsolmagnoEtAl">{{Cite book
  | last = Consolmagno
  | first = Guy
  | coauthors = Davis, Dan 
  | title = Turn left at Orion: a hundred night sky objects to see in a small telescope
  | publisher = University of Cambridge
  | year = 2005
  | location = Cambridge, United Kingdom
  | pages = 189
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=PexKTfPy3voC&pg=PA189&dq=%22jewel+box%22+cluster&lr=&cd=19#v=onepage&q=%22jewel%20box%22%20cluster&f=false
  | isbn = 0 521 78190 6}}</ref>现在估计，珠宝盒星团大约距离地球6,400 [[光年|光年]]<ref name="webda"/>。

==观测==

珠宝盒星团被认为是南天星空最出色的天体之一。<ref name="Kaler">{{Cite book
  | last = Kaler
  | first = James B.
  | title = Stars and their spectra: an introduction to the spectral sequence
  | publisher = University of Cambridge
  | year = 1989
  | pages = 13
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=ycLg34SaJWwC&pg=PA13&dq=%22jewel+box%22+cluster&lr=&cd=6#v=onepage&q=%22jewel%20box%22%20cluster&f=false
  | isbn = 0 521 30494}}</ref>它发出各种各样的颜色，围绕在红橙色的超巨星南十字座κ周围。<ref name="Inglis">{{Cite book
  | last = Inglis
  | first = Mike
  | title = Astronomy of the Milky Way: The observer's guide to the southern Milky Way
  | publisher = Springer
  | year = 2004
  | location = 
  | pages = 78–79
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=1r0qvMjSCGAC&pg=SA3-PA7&dq=%22jewel+box+cluster%22&lr=&cd=15#v=onepage&q=%22jewel%20box%20cluster%22&f=false
  | doi = 
  | id = 
  | isbn = 1-85233-709-5}}</ref>在双筒望远镜或小口径望远镜中，珠宝盒星团就是一个让人印象深刻的天体，但如果使用更大口径的望远镜观测就会得到更好的效果，因为星团的背景云气会变得更加显眼。<ref name="ConsolmagnoEtAl"/>星团最亮的三颗恒星位于同一条直线上并且发出不同颜色的光芒，因此被形象地称为“[[交通灯|交通灯]]”。<ref name="Inglis"/>

寻找星团的方法可以首先寻找[[南十字座|南十字座]]的第二亮星[[十字架三|十字架三]]。珠宝盒星团在十字架三的东面不远处，[[视星等|视星等]]为4等。<ref name="Mobberley">{{Cite book
  | last = Mobberley
  | first = Martin
  | title = The Caldwell Objects
  | publisher = Springer
  | year = 2009
  | location = 
  | pages = 196
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=amPrWoOWgHcC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_navlinks_s#v=onepage&q=&f=false
  | doi = 10.1007/978-1-4419-0326-6
  | isbn = 978-1-4419-0325-9}}</ref>肉眼可以直接看到，但只是一个模糊状的结构，有可能只会当做一颗恒星。<ref name="RidpathTirion">{{Cite book
  | last = [[Ian_Ridpath|Ridpath, Ian]]
  | coauthors = Tirion, Wil
  | title = Stars and Planets
  | pages = 134
  | url = http://books.google.com.au/books?id=-pfuAAAAMAAJ&q=%22kappa+crucis%22+cluster&dq=%22kappa+crucis%22+cluster&lr=&cd=13
  }}</ref>

